## Related Endpoints

### Get Signal Detail
`GET /signals/{id}` - Dapatkan detail spesifik dari sebuah signal termasuk model features dan prediction confidence.

### Price History
`GET /price-history/{symbol}` - Ambil historical price data (OHLCV) untuk instrumen tertentu dengan time filtering support.

### Market Data
`GET /market-data` - Real-time market quotes dan volatility metrics untuk semua supported symbols.

---

## Error Handling

| Status Code | Meaning | Common Cause |
|------------|---------|--------------|
| 400 | Bad Request | Invalid pagination/time parameters, malformed JSON |
| 401 | Unauthorized | Missing or invalid API key |
| 403 | Forbidden | API key has insufficient permissions |
| 404 | Not Found | Resource doesn't exist |
| 429 | Too Many Requests | Rate limit exceeded (100 req/min per API key) |
| 500 | Internal Server Error | Server-side issue. Retry with exponential backoff. |

---

## Rate Limiting & Quotas

- **Rate Limit**: 100 requests per minute per API key
- **Burst**: Up to 10 concurrent requests
- **Response Headers**:
  - `X-RateLimit-Limit: 100`
  - `X-RateLimit-Remaining: 87`
  - `X-RateLimit-Reset: 1711900680`

---

## SDK & Client Libraries

Official SDKs tersedia untuk JavaScript/TypeScript, Python, Go, dan Rust:

- **JavaScript/TypeScript**: `@geonera/api-sdk-js`
- **Python**: `geonera-api-sdk`
- **Go**: `github.com/geonera/api-sdk-go`
- **Rust**: `geonera-api-sdk-rs`

Semua SDK menghandle pagination dan time filtering secara otomatis sesuai best practices.
